snippet.title: Daredevil Dave 2: Motorcycle Mayhem! - iOS Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
App Store Page: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/daredevil-dave-2-motorcycle/id1013225596?ls=1&mt=8

15 minutes of gameplay demonstrating Practice, Mayhem Mode, Motorcycle Golf and Skeeball, and a few movie stuntman levels. There is a huge variety of stunts in Daredevil Dave 2!
